summary: AN ORDINANCE providing for the acquisition by condemnation of land and other property rights in a portion of H. Van Asselt Donation Claim No. 50, being parts of Sections 27, 28, 33 and 34, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W.M., in King County, Washington, lying south of Riverside Addition, according to the plat thereof recorded in Volume 5 of Plats, page 92, in King County, Washington, for open space, park and recreation purposes (East Duwamish Greenbelt) under the Seattle Open Space and Trails Bond Program.
